{"tid":1249441,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"科大交通宇宙第一","createTime":"2019-06-21T17:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T06:22:59.000Z","uid":48452,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"47080a11ac80f413186ffca32e572561058f5015","tid":1249441,"uid":48452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:17:47.000Z","msg":"五點，嶺大學生剛剛起床；科大生已經準備出門了。<br />\n六點，中大學生正在梳洗；科大生已經在等頭班地鐵。<br />\n七點，港大學生仍然悠閒地吃早餐，科大生即將到達牛池灣。<br />\n八點，浸大學生快要到達學校了；科大生正在等車。<br />\n九點，理大生已經準備好上課；科大生依然困在候車人龍當中。<br />\n十點，城大生又抱怨自己太快回到學校；科大生剛剛上了車。<br />\n十一點，所有大學生都下課了。<br />\n<br />\n科大生：『我終於回到學校了！』"},{"pid":"0397d1ff2cfb64c82acfc4760ea840bab307f1af","tid":1249441,"uid":209120,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:30:17.000Z","msg":"彩虹小巴條隊長到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89aa138ff7b6266cf4a54c22d6978d1672d38d05","tid":1249441,"uid":40826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0397d1ff2cfb64c82acfc4760ea840bab307f1af","tid":1249441,"uid":209120,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:30:17.000Z","msg":"彩虹小巴條隊長到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:24:41.000Z","msg":"朝早排巴士好過啦"},{"pid":"d676711258c787178ecbc6a13b733b1d94eaf504","tid":1249441,"uid":253277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:22:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}